external_knowledge:
- 'European region' refers to any country that belongs to the region with the name 'Europe' in the regions table;
- 'most recent climate models' refers to climate models with the highest publication year, as determined by the climate_models table;
- 'accessible data' refers to climate data entries that have a matching data_id in the data_access table;
- 'rainfall' is synonymous with 'precipitation'.
